        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The princess is hosting a festival! Or a competition? A competition festival? You need to collect 15 flower bouquets from three different towns, that much I know! ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Once Upon a Jester",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " sees you play as Jester and Sok, a travelling duo that consists of, well, a jester and, uhh, a sock duck(?). Their goal is to win the festival competition, but oh no, their plan doesn't stop there! Once they're invited to the palace, they can perform at The Royal Theatrical Spectacle where they intend to steal the royal town for, as the game puts, \"SO MUCH MONEY!\". ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y2qzcmqi9f0",
        "html": "<iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Y2qzcmqi9f0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen title=\"Once Upon a Jester - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch\"></iframe>",
        "metadata": {
          "title": "Once Upon a Jester - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch",
          "author_name": "Nintendo of America",
          "author_url": "https://www.youtube.com/c/nintendo",
          "height": 113,
          "width": 200,
